Jason Anthoney Wright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jason_Anthoney_Wright 0 Jason Anthoney "JAW" Wright is an English music, TV/Film producer, writer, actor and singer. He is widely known in the U.K for his chart hits "Reset 2 Zero", "I Wud If I Cud" and "No Me Without U". His Album "Feet on the Ground" was well received globally and often his music is still played on national and international radios.
